POlylang lets us create korean versions of all the pieces of our content we have on our website. 

For categories, we Add New Category 
Name: intro-kr 
Slug: intro-kr 
Parent Category: None
Description: leave blank
Click Add New Category

Do this for each i.e. locations-kr, menu-kr

Then go into Posts and click the + symbol under the Korean flag. Add in teh correct Korean title and the price. You can see it already has the photo attached. Also put it into intro-kr category. Do this for each post. 